---
title: Go Green Opt In
layout: default
hasHeader: true
hasUnauthFooter: true
altNav: true
hasScript:
  - profile
---
<div class="profile">
  <section class="container--base gray">
    <div class="container margin-large">
      <div class="row section-header">
        <div class="col-md-10 margin-large">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-2 col-sm-2 col-md-1 col-lg-1 padding-none">
              <img src="/images/icon-svgs/go-green.svg" alt="Plan Support" class="img-responsive go-green-img">
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-10 col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-11">
              <h2 class="h3 medium margin-small">Go Green: Paperless Document Delivery</h2>
              <p>Select the plan materials you want to sign up for paperless delivery per the terms and conditions below.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="row" id="mail-preferences-selector">
            <div class="col-md-12">{{> gg-card optin="true" full-width="true" splash="true" saved="true"}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="row" id="mail-preferences-selector2">
            <div class="col-md-12">{{> gg-card ship="true" full-width="true" uniqueId="true" splash="true"}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <p class="margin-none">Note: it may take up to two mail cycles for your updated delivery preferences to take effect.  Your mailing cycle-the length of time between documents-varies by document.  When the paper mailings stop, you will receive an email notification alerting you that a new document has been posted to your online account.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
{{> questions }}
